Gorgeous @kanizrabbii in our Sharara set from the Gulzar collection 🌸

Drenched in deep emerald tones and adorned with a profusion of hand-embroidered florals, this ensemble brings together the romance of roses and the richness of tradition.
The intricately detailed neckline, paired with a flowing dupatta and flared sharara pants, makes it perfect for festive soirées or intimate celebrations.
